Odaily Planet Daily News Cryptocurrency payment solution provider Alchemy Pay released its 2025 strategic roadmap, announcing its transformation from a crypto payment gateway to a global financial center, mainly including: 
1. The regulatory priority growth model is accelerating in South Korea, Australia and other regions, and plans to expand wallets, public chains and DEX partners to the ecosystem; 
2. Transforming from a payment gateway to a global financial center supporting risk-weighted assets, Alchemy Pay will no longer be limited to the payment platform positioning, and will cooperate with RWA service providers in the future to promote RWA investment; 
3. Alchemy Chain will develop into a public blockchain built around stablecoins, aggregating the liquidity and utility of major global and local stablecoins such as USDT and USDC in different blockchain networks; 
4. Artificial intelligence encrypted payment, an AI payment product is in the works, with the goal of becoming the standard payment infrastructure for the AI ​​Agent ecosystem.
